le based method is 3.3 our results indicate that incorporating rule based definitions in information retrieval methods can improve search for relevant publications view the sweetinfo project back to search results information last updated fri oct 28 2011 make corrections to this publication go stanford biomedical infomatics only all of stanford school of medicine contact information maps & information site map stanford university
